Privacy Policy

NextFerryTO is provided by Alex MacDonald at no cost and is intended for use as is.

This page informs visitors of my policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information for anyone using NextFerryTO ("the Service").

Information Collection

NextFerryTO does not collect, store, or transmit any personally identifiable information.

The app uses your device's location, with your permission, solely to calculate walking, biking, and transit times to the nearest ferry dock. This location data is processed entirely on your device and is never transmitted to me or stored anywhere.

The app does not automatically collect log data such as crash reports. The Apple App Store itself may collect crash reports and make them available to me, but only if you have given prior consent through your device settings.

Third-Party Links

NextFerryTO links to the City of Toronto website for ferry schedules and ticket purchases. If you tap one of these links, you'll be directed to that site. These external sites are not operated by me, and I have no control over and assume no responsibility for their content, privacy policies, or practices. I encourage you to review the privacy policy of any third-party site you visit.

This policy is effective as of 2026-07-18.

